description:
For the folks who think the face cloths are anything other than a symbol of obedience.
Shit doesn’t protect against diseases,
It’s not designed to. 
In virology the docs wear full hazmat suits. 
That’s the only way you’re gonna stop something literally microscopic from entering your system. 
Our dainty little custom polkadotted cloth masks offer even less protection than a real medical mask. 
Stop kidding yourself,
It’s about your obedience not your safety. 
Or wear a hazmat suit if you’re really that scared of a virus with a 1% mortality rate.
